ezha 2”等电影。 。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 05:17:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-lunar-new-year-holiday-box-office-takings-hit-record-high-13-bln-2025-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>丰田建立全资EV，中国电池单元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-set-up-wholly-owned-ev-battery-unit-china-2025-02-05/</link><description>全球最畅销的汽车制造商周三表示，丰田汽车将在上海建立一家全资公司，为雷克萨斯品牌开发和生产电动汽车和电池，生产将于2027年开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 04:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-set-up-wholly-owned-ev-battery-unit-china-2025-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国钨生产商的股票在北京的最新出口途中集会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shares-china-tungsten-producers-rally-beijings-latest-export-curbs-2025-02-05/</link><description>中国主要的钨生产商的股票周三集会，因为在为期一周的农历新年假期后的第一天，北京对北京最新的关键矿产出口管制做出了反应。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 03:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shares-china-tungsten-producers-rally-beijings-latest-export-curbs-2025-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>黄金在中国关税战争中的历史最高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-rises-all-time-high-sino-us-tariff-war-2025-02-05/</link><description>金价在周三创下了创纪录的高度，这是由于担心北京对美国进口的新美国对中国商品的关税的关税而担心美国和中国之间的新贸易战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 03:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-rises-all-time-high-sino-us-tariff-war-2025-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：东帝汶在主要天然气项目上比中国公司更喜欢澳大利亚，总统说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/east-timor-favours-australia-over-chinese-firms-major-gas-project-president-says-2025-02-05/</link><description>它的总裁说，东帝汶希望与澳大利亚和伍德赛德能源公司合作，而日本的大阪天然气对中国公司的大阪天然气表示有兴趣发展停滞的日出天然气领域。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 03:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/east-timor-favours-australia-over-chinese-firms-major-gas-project-president-says-2025-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国邮政服务暂停了来自中国的传入套餐，香港</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-postal-service-suspends-incoming-packages-china-hong-kong-2025-02-05/</link><description>USPS表示，这种变化不会影响来自中国和香港的字母和“公寓”的流动。它没有立即评论这是否与特朗普的变化有关，以结束从中国和其他国家的De Minimis发货。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 02:35:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-postal-service-suspends-incoming-packages-china-hong-kong-2025-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>在美国原油库存，中国关税战争中，石油降低了</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-little-changed-market-shrugs-off-china-tariffs-iran-pressure-supports-2025-02-05/</link><description>油价周三滑行，因为美国的股票上涨，市场担心新的中级美国贸易战抵消了总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的重新推动，以消除伊朗原油出口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 02:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-little-changed-market-shrugs-off-china-tariffs-iran-pressure-supports-2025-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>Caixin PMI显示，中国的服务活动在较慢的速度下增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-grows-slower-pace-caixin-pmi-shows-2025-02-05/</link><description>私营部门的一项调查显示，中国的服务活动在一月份的速度较慢，农历新年假期恶化，但商业情绪改善了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:56:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-grows-slower-pace-caixin-pmi-shows-2025-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>Semafor报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trump-administration-considers-adding-shein-temu-forced-labor-list-semafor-2025-02-05/</link><description>Semafor周二报道，美国正在讨论是否将中国电子商务零售商Shein和Temu添加到国土安全部（DHS）的“强迫劳动”名单。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:46:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trump-administration-considers-adding-shein-temu-forced-labor-list-semafor-2025-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉为中国的3型购买者提供保险补贴</titl